OL,6,FInflation is almost "guaranteed" to
OL,7,Fcome down rapidly this year unless
OL,8,Fthere is a new, unexpected global
OL,9,Fevent, the Governor of the Bank of
OL,10,FEngland has told MPs.
OL,12,FAndrew Bailey said there would be a
OL,13,F"very powerful unwinding" of inflation
OL,14,Fthroughout the year, which would only
OL,15,Fbe derailed if there is a new external
OL,16,Fshock.
OL,18,FThe Bank said it is staying "watchful"
OL,19,Fand emphasised that there remains
OL,20,F"substantial remaining uncertainty"
OL,21,Fover domestic inflation.
OL,3,CUK Inflation on track to fall but Bank
OL,4,Cremains 'watchful'
